{"tid":1882913,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李蘊「Cream」隊友移居愛爾蘭","createTime":"2020-02-16T14:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T20:43:27.000Z","uid":41343,"like":12,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"f606de706c08453c55172e7f09f605edca5dcf63","tid":1882913,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T14:33:38.000Z","msg":"咁多年嚟香港人可以話係睇住佢長大，眨吓眼Renee已經28歲，2016年嘅時候Renee同拍拖三年嘅內地金融才俊羅章冠結婚，同年5月誕下囡囡晞晞後，前年再誕下囝囝小新，三年抱兩，湊成一個「好」字。榮升媽媽之後，Renee全副心機都擺晒喺一對仔女身上，社交網站幾乎每張相都係同一對仔女嘅甜蜜合照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2560000/2564978/83895250_185861952628329_3192979479051295531_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2560000%2F2564978%2F83895250_185861952628329_3192979479051295531_n_600.jpg&h=492a1e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2560000/2564978/83957836_594611698060415_2053647368922507263_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2560000%2F2564978%2F83957836_594611698060415_2053647368922507263_n_600.jpg&h=b14b1a3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做全職媽媽嘅Renee已經甚少喺現身幕前，不過大家對佢嘅動向一啲都唔陌生。相反，當年組合Cream嘅另外兩位成員好似喺組合解散之後就消聲匿跡，到底依家過成點呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2560000/2564978/TUNGSTAR182615_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2560000%2F2564978%2FTUNGSTAR182615_600.jpg&h=c1ee83d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中一位現年25歲嘅成員陳曉彤（Hilda），原來2007年佢決定搬去愛爾蘭繼續佢嘅學業，喺當地學習音樂，之後喺科克音樂學院以一等榮譽完成學位。受到音樂教師嘅啟發，佢決定繼續跟隨音樂教師嘅歌唱生涯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2560000/2564978/80188792_3111600295534185_371577729813839872_o_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2560000%2F2564978%2F80188792_3111600295534185_371577729813839872_o_600.jpg&h=87d0044e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5315aa27a4d71af2f7fa7a27bddc6316fe4ced68","tid":1882913,"uid":41343,"like":37,"dislike":33,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"男朋友都係外國人，喺當地落地生根。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2560000/2564978/802_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2560000%2F2564978%2F802_600.jpg&h=da59f61d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2560000/2564978/81883581_3111596682201213_6718919161369591808_o_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2560000%2F2564978%2F81883581_3111596682201213_6718919161369591808_o_600.jpg&h=9f7f1e0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2560000/2564978/36817684_2158877524139805_5842371015484637184_o_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2560000%2F2564978%2F36817684_2158877524139805_5842371015484637184_o_600.jpg&h=51d526cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2560000/2564978/52605239_2522714711089416_392764833549778944_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2560000%2F2564978%2F52605239_2522714711089416_392764833549778944_n_600.jpg&h=871300f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b0f67a3f262fd9e48007c5152144170112a11cd","tid":1882913,"uid